{"comments":"Transform Gizmo — Pure state machine for 3D manipulation handles.\n\n## Design Philosophy\nGizmos are PURE STATE MACHINES. Visual geometry is derived from state.\nNo FFI. Drag events come in as messages, state updates purely,\ngizmo geometry is rendered through the standard Scene3D pipeline.\n\n## Three.js Parity\n- TransformControls mode: translate/rotate/scale\n- Space: local/world\n- Axis highlighting on hover\n- Snapping (deferred to Phase 5)\n\n## Industry Standard\n- Universal gizmo (all transforms in one)\n- Per-axis and per-plane manipulation\n- Visual feedback during drag\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[118,18],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Scene3D/Gizmo.purs","start":[118,3]},"title":"TranslateMode"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[119,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Scene3D/Gizmo.purs","start":[119,3]},"title":"RotateMode"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[120,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Scene3D/Gizmo.purs","start":[120,3]},"title":"ScaleMode"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","Scene3D","Gizmo"],"GizmoMode"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[122,44],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Scene3D/Gizmo.purs","start":[122,1]},"title":"eqGizmoMode"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","Scene3D","Gizmo"],"GizmoMode"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[127,31],"name":"../..